Start time : 06/07/2022 09:00 UTC Service impact : We observe temporary 404 on GET method and 503 on PUT method, both due to misplaced objects. Ongoing actions : Our teams investigate to resolve the situation.

Start time : 18/07/2022 07:00 UTC End time : 18/07/2022 09:00 UTC Service impact : Customers with i1 flavor instances could not be migrated and therefore remain in the defective rack, during the maintenance the hosts will be powered off and therefore instances will be offline for arround 2 hours. Service improvement : The objectif of this operation is to do a replacement of defect in the rack cooling system.

Start time : 21/07/2022 05:00 UTC End time : 21/07/2022 06:00 UTC Service impact : There will be a 3 mins downtime during which the write access , read/write access will be unavailable. Service improvement: The aim of this maintenance is to migrate all PostgreSQL databases from one cluster to another.
